+**Status legend:** `- [x] ⚪ Pending` · `- [ ] 🟡 Provisional` · `- [ ] 🟧 Local-Implemented` · `- [ ] 🟣 Lane-Promoted` · `- [ ] ✅ Production-Ready`.
