+## Execution Plan
+
+### Touched Surfaces
+
+- `foundation_documentation/todos/completed/TODO-v1-pre-mvp-web-small-fixes-intake.md`
+- `foundation_documentation/todos/completed/TODO-v1-web-bootstrap-branding-continuity.md`
